  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub from the rendered outputs. Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">What does 3.5 years of riding <em class=\"\">look like</em> if you average it all together? This takes the helmet-cam footage from years of motorcycle trips and runs it through a battery of meta-visualization techniques — pulling images out of the footage that no single frame contains.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Salavon-style average of thousands of frames — the road, horizon, and the dark wedge of the bike emerging as a ghost\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-average.png\" alt=\"Salavon-style average of thousands of frames — the road, horizon, and the dark wedge of the bike emerging as a ghost\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-average.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-average.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-average.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-average.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Salavon-style average of thousands of frames — the road, horizon, and the dark wedge of the bike emerging as a ghost\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×360\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Salavon-style average of thousands of frames — the road, horizon, and the dark wedge of the bike emerging as a ghost</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Frame averaging</strong> (after Jason Salavon) stacks thousands of frames into one — the constants of riding (road below, sky above, the fairing) resolve into a soft ghost while everything transient blurs away. Run it per year and you can watch the ghost shift as the routes and seasons change:</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The average of every 2021 frame\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2021.png\" alt=\"The average of every 2021 frame\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2021.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2021.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2021.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2021.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The average of every 2021 frame\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×360\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The average of every 2021 frame</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The average of every 2022 frame\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2022.png\" alt=\"The average of every 2022 frame\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2022.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2022.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2022.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2022.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The average of every 2022 frame\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.88deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×360\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The average of every 2022 frame</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The average of every 2024 frame\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2024.png\" alt=\"The average of every 2024 frame\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2024.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2024.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2024.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-2024.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The average of every 2024 frame\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.37deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×360\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The average of every 2024 frame</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The years side by side, as one composite strip\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-years.png\" alt=\"The years side by side, as one composite strip\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-years.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-years.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-years.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/salavon-years.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The years side by side, as one composite strip\" width=\"1280\" height=\"200\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1280×200\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The years side by side, as one composite strip</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Slit-scan</strong> takes a single column from every frame and lays them side by side, turning a whole ride into a striated band of color and light — both horizontally and vertically.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Slit-scan: one column per frame, a whole ride compressed into a band\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan.png\" alt=\"Slit-scan: one column per frame, a whole ride compressed into a band\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Slit-scan: one column per frame, a whole ride compressed into a band\" width=\"2387\" height=\"360\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.88deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2387×360\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Slit-scan: one column per frame, a whole ride compressed into a band</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Vertical slit-scan variant\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan-vertical.png\" alt=\"Vertical slit-scan variant\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan-vertical.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan-vertical.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan-vertical.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/slit-scan-vertical.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Vertical slit-scan variant\" width=\"640\" height=\"1085\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"640×1085\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vertical slit-scan variant</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Dusk gradient — the color of the light, averaged across the golden-hour rides\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-gradient.png\" alt=\"Dusk gradient — the color of the light, averaged across the golden-hour rides\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-gradient.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-gradient.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-gradient.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-gradient.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Dusk gradient — the color of the light, averaged across the golden-hour rides\" width=\"2400\" height=\"804\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.76deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2400×804\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Dusk gradient — the color of the light, averaged across the golden-hour rides</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Cinema redux</strong> shrinks every frame to a tile and tiles them into a single mosaic — the entire footage archive as one dense image, a barcode of where I've been.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Cinema redux — every frame as a tile, the whole archive in one mosaic\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux.png\" alt=\"Cinema redux — every frame as a tile, the whole archive in one mosaic\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Cinema redux — every frame as a tile, the whole archive in one mosaic\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2510\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3000×2510\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Cinema redux — every frame as a tile, the whole archive in one mosaic</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Cinema redux, frame variant — a denser grid\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux-frames.png\" alt=\"Cinema redux, frame variant — a denser grid\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux-frames.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux-frames.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux-frames.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/cinema-redux-frames.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Cinema redux, frame variant — a denser grid\" width=\"4000\" height=\"3434\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.69deg;\" data-dimensions=\"4000×3434\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Cinema redux, frame variant — a denser grid</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A contact-grid of frames pulled from the rides\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/frame-grid.png\" alt=\"A contact-grid of frames pulled from the rides\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/frame-grid.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/frame-grid.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/frame-grid.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/frame-grid.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"A contact-grid of frames pulled from the rides\" width=\"4506\" height=\"3870\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.73deg;\" data-dimensions=\"4506×3870\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">A contact-grid of frames pulled from the rides</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Dusk anthology — a tall contact sheet of golden-hour frames\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-contact.png\" alt=\"Dusk anthology — a tall contact sheet of golden-hour frames\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-contact.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-contact.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-contact.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/motorcycle-viz/dusk-contact.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Dusk anthology — a tall contact sheet of golden-hour frames\" width=\"1940\" height=\"5684\" style=\"--splay-rot:1.7deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1940×5684\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Dusk anthology — a tall contact sheet of golden-hour frames</figcaption>\n</figure>",
